Mini-PowerSchool

2021-09-21

Description

For this project, I created a mobile app to calculate class grades. It is hard to calculate our grades using a simple calculator, since different scores have different weight. Thus, I developed this small program to help my classmates calculate their grades and also use their estimated final score to predict whether or not they can get an A.

Simple GUI

pictures may load a little bit slowly

import tkinter as tk
from tkinter import messagebox
import xlrd
import xlsxwriter
import shutil
import openpyxl
import time
from PIL import Image,ImageTk

window = tk.Tk()
window.title(‘Mini-Powerschool’)
window.geometry(“300x485”)
window.resizable(0,0)

load = Image.open(‘ico.png’)
render = ImageTk.PhotoImage(load)
img = tk.Label(window, image=render)
img.place(x=-3,y=-80)

tk.Label(window, text=’User name:’).place(x=50, y=300)
tk.Label(window, text=’Password:’).place(x=55, y=360)
var_user_name = tk.StringVar()
entry_user_name = tk.Entry(window, textvariable=var_user_name)
entry_user_name.place(x=130, y=300)
var_user_pass = tk.StringVar()
entry_password = tk.Entry(window, textvariable=var_user_pass, show=’*’)
entry_password.place(x=130, y=360)

flag = 5
def login():
  global flag
  user_name = var_user_name.get()
  user_password = var_user_pass.get()
  path = “D:/桌面/仿powerschool/数据库/“ + user_name + “.xlsx”
  try:
    xl = xlrd.open_workbook(path)
  except:
    tk.Label(window, text=’Invalid user name’, font=(‘Times New Roman’, 10), width=30, height=2).place(x=80, y=100)
  f = open(‘D:/桌面/仿powerschool/黑名单/黑名单.txt’, ‘r’)
  blackls = f.read()
  if blackls.find(user_name) != -1:
    tk.messagebox.showerror(message=’Your account was locked, plase contact admin.\nE-mail: bixcmlc@126.com‘)
    f.close()
    window.quit()

  table = xl.sheet_by_name(u”密码”)
  password = table.cell(0,0).value
  if user_password == password:
    tk.Label(window, text=’You have successfully loged in’, font=(“Times New Roman”, 10), width=30, height=2).place(x=60, y=230)
  else:
    tk.Label(window, text=”Invalid password”, font=(‘Times New Roman’, 10), width=30, height=2).place(x=60, y=300)
    flag -= 1
    var = tk.StringVar()
    var.set(‘You have ‘ + str(flag) + ‘ chance(s) left’)
    tk.Label(window, textvariable=var, width=20, height=3).place(x=60, y=340)
    if flag == 0:
      f = open(‘D:/桌面/仿powerschool/黑名单/黑名单.txt’, ‘w’)
      f.write(user_name)
      f.close()
      tk.messagebox.showerror(message=’You are failed to log in.\nYour account is locked, please contact admin.\nE-mail: bjxcmlc@126.com‘)
      window.quit()

def signup():
  sign_up_window = tk.Toplevel(window)
  sign_up_window.geometry(‘300x200’)
  sign_up_window.title(‘Sign up’)
  tk.Label(sign_up_window, text=’User name:’).place(x=20, y=40)
  tk.Label(sign_up_window, text=’Password:’).place(x=25, y=80)
  tk.Label(sign_up_window, text=’Confirm password:’).place(x=15, y=120)
  var_user_name = tk.StringVar()
  entry_user_name = tk.Entry(sign_up_window, textvariable=var_user_name)
  entry_user_name.place(x=100, y=40)

  var_user_pass1 = tk.StringVar()
  entry_password1 = tk.Entry(sign_up_window, textvariable=var_user_pass1)
  entry_password1.place(x=100, y=80)

  var_user_pass2 = tk.StringVar()
  entry_password2 = tk.Entry(sign_up_window, textvariable=var_user_pass2)
  entry_password2.place(x=130, y=120)

  def confirm():
    user_name = var_user_name.get()
    user_pass1 = var_user_pass1.get()
    user_pass2 = var_user_pass2.get()
    cpath = user_name + “.xlsx”
    cpassword = user_pass1
    mpath1 = r”D:\桌面\仿powerschool\“ + cpath
    mpath2 = r”D:\桌面\仿powerschool\数据库”
    if user_pass1 == user_pass2:
      tk.messagebox.showinfo(message=’You have successfully signed up’)
      sign_up_window.destroy()
      userfile = xlsxwriter.Workbook(cpath)
      worksheet = userfile.add_worksheet(u”密码”)
      worksheet.write(“A1”,cpassword)
      userfile.close()
      shutil.move(mpath1,mpath2)
    else:
      tk.messagebox.showinfo(message=’The two passwords are different, please check’)
  def cancel():
    sign_up_window.destroy()
  
  tk.Button(sign_up_window, text=’Cancel’, command=cancel).place(x=50, y=160)
  tk.Button(sign_up_window, text=’Confirm’, command=confirm).place(x=130, y=160)
  sign_up_window.mainloop()

tk.Button(window,text=’Login’, command=login).place(x=75, y=410)
tk.Button(window, text=’Sign up’, command=signup).place(x=175, y=410)

window.mainloop()

print(“ “)

  par = input(“please input participation&citizenship grade(s):”)
  PA = input(“please input progressive assessment grade(s):”)
  SA = input(“please input summative assessment grade(s):”)
  final = input(“please input final exam grade:”)
  conpensation = 1
  par_weight = 0.1
  PA_weight = 0.3
  SA_weight = 0.3
  final_weight = 0.3
  x = par.split()
  y = PA.split()
  z = SA.split()
  if x[0] == “-1”:
    par_weight = 0
    conpensation -= 0.05
  if y[0] == “-1”:
    PA_weight = 0
    conpensation -= 0.3
  if z[0] == “-1”:
    SA_weight = 0
    conpensation -= 0.35
  if final == “-1”:
    final_weight = 0
    conpensation -= 0.3
  par_grade = 0
  PA_grade = 0
  SA_grade = 0
  for a in range(len(x)):
    par_grade += (eval(x[a])/len(x))
  for b in range(len(y)):
    PA_grade += (eval(y[b])/len(y))
  for c in range(len(z)):
    SA_grade += (eval(z[c])/len(z))
  final_exam = eval(final)
  grade = (final_exam*final_weight + par_grade*par_weight + PA_gradePA_weight + SA_gradeSA_weight) / conpensation
  print(“your grade is：”, grade)
  grade = round(grade)

    level = “A”

    level = “B”

    level = “C”
  if 60 <= grade < 65:
    level = “D”
  if grade < 60:
    level = “F”
  print(“最终成绩为：”, grade, level)
  print(“you can change/drop/recover your grade”, “\n”)

      if x[0] == “-1” :
        par_weight = 0
        conpensation -= 0.05
      if y[0] == “-1” :
        PA_weight = 0
        conpensation -= 0.3

        SA_weight = 0
        conpensation -= 0.35

        final_weight = 0

      if final_exam != -1 :
        final_weight = 0.3

        del y[int(change_ls[2])-1]

        del z[int(change_ls[2])-1]
      if x == []:
        par_weight = 0
        conpensation -= 0.05
      if y == []:
        PA_weight = 0
        conpensation -= 0.3
      if z == []:
        SA_weight = 0
        conpensation -= 0.35

        par_weight = 0
